			<div id="homeDescr">
				<span class="title">Maps</span><br>				
				With all the talk of globalization it is easy 
				to forget that at the very core of the concept is a notion of 
				geographical location. Globalization involves connections between 
				at least two places and the first step in our understanding must 
				be an appreciation of what this means in a concrete sense of space.
				<a href="http://qed.princeton.edu/index.php/MG/Maps">More...</a>			</div>
